Title: Class Specifiers
Crumbs:%ROOT%, Programming/UnrealArchitecture/Reference,  Programming/UnrealArchitecture/Reference, Programming/UnrealArchitecture/Reference/Classes
Description: Keywords used when declaring gameplay classes to specify how the class behaves with various aspects of the engine and editor.
Availability:Public
Version: 4.9

[EXCERPT:main]
When declaring classes, specifiers can be added to the declaration to control how the class behaves with various 
aspects of the engine and editor.

